data.text:
The following undergraduate students were cited for academic achievement during the Spring 2024 semester at Central Connecticut State University, New Britain.

Dean's List recognition is awarded to full-time matriculated undergraduate students each semester who carry at least 12 academic credits, earned a 3.50 GPA (out of a possible 4.0), and who did not have any incomplete grades for the semester at the time grades were processed.
